set_language_title~==~Set Your Default Language
set_language_help~==~Specify the language you want to see your web pages in. To do so, select your preferred language and click <B>Set Language</B>. Each time you visit our site later you will not need to set your language, the system will keep your selected default language using a cookie on your computer.
submit_button~==~<A HREF="#" onclick="document.Language_Form.submit(); return false;"><B>Set My Default Language</B></A>
reset_button~==~<A HREF="#" onclick="document.Language_Form.reset(); return false;"><B>Reset</B></A>
cancel_button~==~<A HREF="javascript:history.go(-1)"><b>Cancel</b></A>
